-- Xstrata to respond to Glencore final offer by Sept 24
-- 
-- Mon Sep 10, 2012 2:47am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/09/10/us-glencore-xstrata-response-idUSBRE88907T20120910

 

 LONDON  (Reuters) - Miner Xstrata said on Monday its independent directors would respond by 0600 GMT on September 24 to a revised, $36 billion takeover offer from trader Glencore, its largest shareholder. 
 "The independent non-executive directors will consider carefully the proposal received and consult with major shareholders before responding," Xstrata said in a statement. (Reporting by  Clara Ferreira-Marques )